There are three redundant data types in the program:

1. short
2. volatile short
3. short fn3(p1)

The program uses the short data type several times, but it is not defined explicitly as a typedef. The volatile short data type is not defined explicitly either, but it is used in the m[5][8] array, which is volatile. The short fn3(p1) data type is defined explicitly as a function type.
